comments: Brown (TOR) places his hands on Young's (ATL) back, but he does not extend into him and dislodge him from his position.
Olynyk (TOR) places his hand against Bey's (ATL) side and marginal contact occurs during Bey's drive to the basket.
Brown (TOR) places his forearm to Bey's (ATL) front to brace for the ensuing contact and the contact is marginal.
Olynyk (TOR) extends his arm into Bey's (ATL) back and the contact affects his layup attempt.
Trent Jr. (TOR) establishes himself in Johnson's (ATL) path and the two players briefly engage and disengage.
Hunter (ATL) places a hand on Olynyk's (TOR) back with minimal extension and the contact does not affect Olynyk's shot attempt.
Barnes (TOR) cleanly blocks the shot attempt before it touches the backboard.
Quickley (TOR) initiates contact with Hunter's (ATL) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Olynyk (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position Murray's (ATL) path and marginal contact occurs when Murray moves to the side to attempt to avoid contact.
Johnson (ATL) contests the driving shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Quickley's (TOR) arm after the release.
Hunter (ATL) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds and TOR should retain possession.
Capela (ATL) moves to his right when Trent Jr. (TOR) is moving around the screen, but Capela avoids initiating any illegal contact.
Murray (ATL) steps out of bounds at the start of his dribble.
Young (ATL) commits a take foul on Brown (TOR).
Olynyk (TOR) is moving alongside Bey's (ATL) path when Bey loses control of his own dribble.
Barnes (TOR) reaches in and makes incidental contact with the part of Young's (ATL) hand on the ball.
